Gynecological aspects of retroperitoneal diseases (author's transl). Current literature was reviewed for gynecological aspects of retroperitoneal diseases. Taking into account the original histological findings retroperitoneal diseases were divided into the following groups from a gynecological point of view: 1. Malignant and benign primary retroperitoneal tumors 2. retroperitoneal organs 3. malignant and benign tumors of retroperitoneal organs 4. retroperitoneal gynecological structures 5. retroperitoneal metastases 6. other retroperitoneal diseases.